2009-05-03 Paolo Mantegazza <mantegazza@aero.polimi.it>

	* base/include/rtai_lxrt.h: syscalls list reordered to allow
	  overruns checks server call function, renamed server create,
	  legacy maintained, delete RTAI task extension when exiting the
	  Linux syscall server.
	* base/schede/sys.c: ensure the linux syscall server is forced to
	  exit when deleting its parent RTAI extension.
	* base/schede/api.c: checks Linux async syscalls overruns.

2009-04-30 Paolo Mantegazza <mantegazza@aero.polimi.it>

	* base/include/rtai_lxrt.h: linux server reworked to need no info
	  about registers structure.
	* base/schede/api.c: linux server reworked to allow server task
	  working with no info about registers structure.

